partnerDetails.about: Sphere Electrical Wholesalers CC was incorporated in 2001. We trade as an Electrical Wholesaler. Our aim is to provide excellent service to all our clients at all time The owner Mr N Goncalves has been involved in the electrical field since 1989. We deal in all domestic, commercial and industrial goods.
